<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="5855">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$da-fei-67-45" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/da-fei-67-45" class="zg-link" title="达菲">达菲</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qiu-shan-ling-7" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qiu-shan-ling-7" class="zg-link" title="秋山澪">秋山澪</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shi-bin-hun" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shi-bin-hun" class="zg-link" title="HySy">HySy</a></span>
